Summary: Object grew from small to a larger size then disappeared.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was sitting outside looking at the stars when I looked northwest I seen a white glow which grew in size ( small like a pin head they like a dime size ) then just disappeared. It was like seeing a white fireworks burst and how they grow but without any sparks or falling debris. No fade out just gone.
